    And the response should contain 3 client records
    And the response should contain pagination metadata

  # Why: Core deletion
  @key-example @smoke
  Scenario: Deleting a client removes it from the store
    Given a client "Jane Smith" exists
    When I delete the client
    Then the response should indicate successful deletion with no content
    When I retrieve the client by their ID
    Then the response should indicate the resource was not found

  # Why: Filtered list — status filtering
  @key-example
  Scenario: Listing clients filtered by status returns only matching records
    Given a client with status "active" exists
    And a client with status "suspended" exists
    When I list clients filtered by status "active"
